#

Caprese Salad with a Twist

10 min
$8.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Salad

Tags:

EasyFreshSalad

Description

A refreshing take on the classic Caprese salad, with a zingy twist that elevates your taste experience.

Ingredients

  • fresh tomatoes: 2 large
  • mozzarella cheese: 8 oz
  • fresh basil leaves: 1 cup
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • pine nuts: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • balsamic glaze: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
